    <segment id="72">, 58 anos</segment>
    <segment id="73">, nos bailes da Capital.</segment>
    <segment id="74">Mas o romance do casal engrenou mesmo nas aulas de tango.</segment>
    <segment id="75">Todas as segundas-feiras</segment>
